            "type": "text",
            "text": "Qwen Image Edit Plus is a specialized model designed for image manipulation, with a focus on text addition and editing. It supports various image formats, provides low-latency responses, and is optimized for scalability in API environments. Key features include precise text placement, font customization, and batch processing capabilities, making it suitable for high-throughput applications."
